item.title: The Sixth Wonder of the World
item.description: The Colossus of Rhodes *was* a statue of the god Helios in the greek city of Rhodes on the island of the same name. It was bigly, and the best. Everyone Knows it. He knows it, and they know it. I'm a genius, so I know it.
